high_descs: Take a small step forward then turn right to face the stove.
Pick up the dirty pan on the back left burner.
Turn right and move to your right until you're in front of the sink then walk to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Put the pan in the top portion of  the fridge on the bottom shelf then close the doors.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan in the fridge.

high_descs: Pick up a dirty pan from the stove
Wash the pan in the sink
Place the pan in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Wash a dirty pan and set in a fridge

high_descs: Turn right to face the stove.
Pick up the pan from the back left corner of the stove.
Turn around and move forward, then turn left to go to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink.
Go to the fridge behind you.
Put the pan in the fridge.
